<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Human Clinic — Mídia Offline 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --cream: #F5F2EC;
  --dark: #111010;
  --gold: #B8965A;
  --gold-light: #D4B07C;
  --gold-pale: #F0E6D3;
  --warm-white: #FDFAF5;
  --mid: #6B6560;
  --line: rgba(184,150,90,0.25);
  --red-accent: #8B3A2A;
  --green-accent: #2A5C45;
  --green-light: #EAF2EC;
  --red-light: #F5EAE8;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--dark);
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ─── HEADER ─── */
.site-header {
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--warm-white);
  padding: 0 60px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 64px;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
}

.logo {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--gold-light);
}

.header-nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 32px;
  list-style: none;
}

.header-nav a {
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color .2s;
}
.header-nav a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }

.header-badge {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .06em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
  border: .5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

/* ─── HERO ─── */
.hero {
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--warm-white);
  padding: 100px 60px 80px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-bg-line {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.hero-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
}

.hero-label::before {
  content: '';
  display: block;
  width: 32px;
  height: .5px;
  background: var(--gold);
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.0;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
  max-width: 760px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.hero-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--gold-light);
}

.hero-sub {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
  max-width: 520px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}

.kpi-strip {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border: .5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  max-width: 800px;
}

.kpi-block {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
  padding: 24px 28px;
  transition: background .2s;
}
.kpi-block:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); }

.kpi-n {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.kpi-l {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
  letter-spacing: .03em;
}

/* ─── INSIGHT BOX ─── */
.insight {
  background: var(--warm-white);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 20px 28px;
  margin: 60px 60px 0;
  border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.insight-icon {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  background: var(--gold-pale);
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 2px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.insight-icon::after {
  content: '';
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--gold);
  border-radius: 50%;
}

.insight p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--mid);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.insight strong { color: var(--dark); font-weight: 500; }

/* ─── SECTION ─── */
.section {
  padding: 80px 60px;
}

.section + .section {
  border-top: .5px solid var(--line);
}

.section-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.section-number {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 72px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--gold-pale);
  line-height: 1;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.section-meta { flex: 1; }

.section-category {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: .14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.section-title {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.15;
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--mid);
  margin-top: 8px;
  max-width: 560px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* ─── EVENT CARDS ─── */
.events-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2px;
}

.event-row {
  background: var(--warm-white);
  border: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color .2s;
}
.event-row:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
.event-row.open { border-color: var(--gold); }

.event-summary {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 120px;
  gap: 0;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20px 28px;
}

.event-info { }
.event-name {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}
.event-date {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--mid);
}

.event-stat { padding: 0 16px; border-left: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
.event-stat-l { font-size: 11px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.event-stat-v {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1;
}
.event-stat-v.good { color: var(--green-accent); }
.event-stat-v.cost { color: var(--red-accent); }
.event-stat-v.neutral { color: var(--dark); }

.event-badge {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  letter-spacing: .03em;
  text-align: center;
}
.badge-priority { background: #2A5C45; color: #EAF2EC; }
.badge-roi { background: #B8965A; color: #FDF8F0; }
.badge-partner { background: #8B3A2A; color: #F5EAE8; }
.badge-culture { background: #3A4A6B; color: #E8ECF5; }
.badge-vip { background: #4A3A6B; color: #EDE8F5; }

.event-detail {
  display: none;
  padding: 0 28px 24px;
  border-top: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
  margin-top: -1px;
}
.event-row.open .event-detail { display: block; }

.detail-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.detail-box {
  background: var(--cream);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
}

.detail-box-title {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mid);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.detail-items {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 5px;
}

.detail-items li {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--dark);
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 8px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.detail-items li::before {
  content: '';
  width: 4px;
  height: 4px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--gold);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.detail-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--mid);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-top: 14px;
  padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
}

/* ─── FUNNEL VISUAL ─── */
.funnel-section {
  background: var(--dark);
  color: var(--warm-white);
  padding: 80px 60px;
}

.funnel-section .section-number { color: rgba(184,150,90,.2); }
.funnel-section .section-title { color: var(--warm-white); }
.funnel-section .section-category { color: var(--gold); }
.funnel-section .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }

.funnel-visual {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
  gap: 2px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.funnel-step {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}

.funnel-step::after {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute;
  right: -12px;
  top: 40px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
  font-size: 16px;
}
.funnel-step:last-child::after { display: none; }

.funnel-bar-wrap {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.funnel-bar {
  border-radius: 4px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  width: 80%;
}

.funnel-n {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 42px;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1;
  color: var(--gold-light);
}

.funnel-unit {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.funnel-step-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.funnel-step-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
  margin-top: 3px;
}

/* ─── EXPERIENCE CARDS ─── */
.exp-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

.exp-card {
  background: var(--warm-white);
  border: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 28px 24px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
  transition: border-color .2s;
}
.exp-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
.exp-card.hero-card { border: 1.5px solid var(--gold); }

.exp-card-tag {
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: .12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
}

.exp-card-name {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.exp-card-freq {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--mid);
}

.exp-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 8px;
}

.exp-stat {
  background: var(--cream);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 10px 12px;
}

.exp-stat-l { font-size: 11px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.exp-stat-v {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--dark);
}
.exp-stat-v.g { color: var(--green-accent); }
.exp-stat-v.r { color: var(--red-accent); }

.exp-divider { border: none; border-top: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06); }

.exp-funnel {
  display: flex;
  gap: 3px;
}

.exp-funnel-step {
  flex: 1;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.exp-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--mid);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ─── ROI TABLE ─── */
.roi-section { background: var(--warm-white); }

.roi-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 14px;
}

.roi-table thead th {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: .08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--mid);
  font-weight: 400;
  padding: 0 20px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: .5px solid var(--line);
}

.roi-table thead th:not(:first-child) { text-align: right; }

.roi-table tbody tr {
  border-bottom: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05);
  transition: background .15s;
}
.roi-table tbody tr:hover { background: var(--cream); }
.roi-table tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

.roi-table tbody td {
  padding: 16px 20px;
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.roi-table tbody td:not(:first-child) { text-align: right; }

.roi-frente { font-weight: 500; }
.roi-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--mid); margin-top: 2px; }
.val-good { color: var(--green-accent); font-weight: 500; }
.val-cost { color: var(--red-accent); }
.roi-total {
  background: var(--dark) !important;
  color: var(--warm-white);
}
.roi-total td { padding: 20px; }
.roi-total .val-good { color: #7BCCA0; }
.roi-total .val-cost { color: #E0907A; }

/* ─── TIMELINE ─── */
.timeline {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 40px;
}

.timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 6px;
  top: 8px;
  bottom: 8px;
  width: 1px;
  background: var(--line);
}

.tl-item {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 36px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

.tl-dot {
  position: absolute;
  left: -37px;
  top: 5px;
  width: 11px;
  height: 11px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid var(--warm-white);
  outline: 1px solid var(--line);
}

.tl-month {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--dark);
  padding-top: 2px;
}

.tl-period {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--mid);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.tl-content { }

.tl-name {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 400;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.tl-chips {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.chip {
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: .5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);
  color: var(--mid);
}
.chip.cost { border-color: rgba(139,58,42,.3); color: var(--red-accent); }
.chip.leads { border-color: rgba(42,92,69,.3); color: var(--green-accent); }
.chip.focus { border-color: rgba(184,150,90,.4); color: var(--gold); }

.tl-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--mid); line-height: 1.6; }

/* ─── FOOTER ─── */
.site-footer {
  background: var(--dark);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
  padding: 40px 60px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 12px;
}

.footer-logo {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: .1em;
}

/* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.animate { opacity: 0; }
.animate.visible { animation: fadeUp .6s ease forwards; }

/* stagger delays */
.delay-1 { animation-delay: .1s; }
.delay-2 { animation-delay: .2s; }
.delay-3 { animation-delay: .3s; }
.delay-4 { animation-delay: .4s; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .site-header { padding: 0 24px; }
  .header-nav { display: none; }
  .hero { padding: 60px 24px; }
  .kpi-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  .insight { margin: 40px 24px 0; }
  .section { padding: 60px 24px; }
  .funnel-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
  .event-summary { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .exp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .funnel-visual { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); }
  .detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .tl-item { grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr; }
  .site-footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="logo">HUMAN CLINIC SP</div>
  <nav>
    <ul class="header-nav">
      <li><a href="#eventos">Eventos AAA</a></li>
      <li><a href="#experiencias">Experiências</a></li>
      <li><a href="#funil">Funil</a></li>
      <li><a href="#roi">ROI</a></li>
      <li><a href="#calendario">Calendário</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
  <div class="header-badge">Mídia Offline 2026</div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <svg class="hero-bg-line" viewBox="0 0 1400 500" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <line x1="0" y1="500" x2="1400" y2="0" stroke="rgba(184,150,90,0.06)" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="700" y1="500" x2="1400" y2="200" stroke="rgba(184,150,90,0.04)" stroke-width="1"/>
  </svg>
  <div class="hero-label animate">Planejamento estratégico · Dr. Ivan Rollemberg</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title animate delay-1">Mídia <em>offline.</em><br>Menos leads.<br>Mais certos.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub animate delay-2">O offline não compete com o tráfego pago em volume. Compete em qualidade — pacientes que chegam com intenção formada, ciclo de venda mais curto e ticket de R$50–60K.</p>
  <div class="kpi-strip animate delay-3">
    <div class="kpi-block">
      <div class="kpi-n">8–20</div>
      <div class="kpi-l">leads qualificados / mês</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-block">
      <div class="kpi-n">35–55%</div>
      <div class="kpi-l">taxa de fechamento</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-block">
      <div class="kpi-n">R$3,3–7,5M</div>
      <div class="kpi-l">receita potencial / ano</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kpi-block">
      <div class="kpi-n">R$180–400K</div>
      <div class="kpi-l">investimento total / ano</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="insight animate">
  <div class="insight-icon"></div>
  <p>O offline é a única frente onde o Dr. Ivan deixa de ser um anúncio e se torna uma <strong>presença real</strong>. Pacientes que chegam por evento ou indicação fecham mais rápido porque a confiança já foi construída antes do primeiro contato.</p>
</div>

<!-- EVENTOS AAA -->
<section class="section" id="eventos">
  <div class="section-header animate">
    <div class="section-number">01</div>
    <div class="section-meta">
      <div class="section-category">Frente 1 — Eventos externos 2026</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Eventos AAA externos</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Presença nos maiores eventos do universo premium de SP. Estratégia: relacionamento e autoridade — não exposição. Em 2026, o SPFW tem apenas uma edição (outubro). Lollapalooza e Hipismo listados como referência para 2027. Clique em cada evento para ver os detalhes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="events-grid animate delay-1">

    <!-- PORSCHE CUP -->
    <div class="event-row" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="event-summary">
        <div class="event-info">
          <div class="event-name">Porsche Cup Brasil</div>
          <div class="event-date">Etapas em SP: 28/02–01/03 · 28–29/03 (Velocitta) · 05–06/09 · 07–08/11 — Interlagos</div>
        </div>
        <div class="event-stat">
          <div class="event-stat-l">Leads / etapa</div>
          <div class="event-stat-v good">5–10</div>
        </div>
        <div class="event-stat">
          <div class="event-stat-l">Investimento</div>
          <div class="event-stat-v cost">R$0–30K</div>
        </div>
        <div class="event-stat">
          <div class="event-stat-l">Taxa fechamento</div>
          <div class="event-stat-v neutral">40–55%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="event-stat">
          <div class="event-stat-l">Receita potencial</div>
          <div class="event-stat-v good">R$137–302K</div>
        </div>
        <div><span class="event-badge badge-priority">Já presentes</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-detail">
        <div class="detail-grid">
          <div class="detail-box">
            <div class="detail-box-title">Por que Porsche Cup é estratégico</div>
